				  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			        &nbsp; Cheat menu -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Enter the Options screen and then select Pad Config. Hold R2, and press Right, Up, Right, Triangle, X. A sound will confirm correct code entry. On the main menu, there'll be a new cheat option</font>&nbsp;
			        <br>&nbsp; Secret Characters - At the main menu go to select player.Go to create player then enter 'CHEATS BE ON' as the player's name.Now repeat the method with these names - All character cheats -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">BOSS CHEATS</font>&nbsp;
			        <br>&nbsp; Secret Characters - At the main menu go to select player.Go to create player then enter 'CHEATS BE ON' as the player's name.Now repeat the method with these names - Different appearence - -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">TIGER CHEATS</font>&nbsp;
			        <br>&nbsp; Secret Characters - At the main menu go to select player.Go to create player then enter 'CHEATS BE ON' as the player's name.Now repeat the method with these names - Makes your character sharklike -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">SHARK CHEATS</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
